lgaria crushed Serbia in the [[Serbo-Bulgarian War]] of 1885, Bulgaria nearly doubled in size when [[East Rumelia]] was incorporated within its borders. Bulgaria officially annexed it from the [[Ottoman Empire]] in 1885.\n|-\n| {{flagicon image|Zentralamerikanische Gro\u00dfrepublik 1898.svg}} [[Greater Republic of Central America]]\n| {{flagicon image|Flag of El Salvador (1875-1877).svg}} [[El Salvador]]<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Honduras (1866-1898).svg}} [[Honduras]]<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Nicaragua (1858-1889 and 1893-1896).svg}} [[Nicaragua]]<br />Considered joining:<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Costa Rica (1848-1906).svg}} [[Costa Rica]]<br />{{flag|Guatemala}}\n| 1895\u20131898\n| {{yes|Yes <br /> (1896\u20131898)}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flagicon image|US flag 49 stars.svg}} [[United States of America]]\n| {{flagicon image|US flag 49 stars.svg}} [[United States of America]]<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Hawaii.svg}} [[Republic of Hawaii]]\n| 1898\n| {{yes|Yes}}\n| United States annexation of the [[Territory of Hawaii]]\n|}\n\n===20th century===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"130\" | Proposed state\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"150\" | Components\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"70\" | Time period\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"80\" | Successful?\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"620\" | Notes\n|-\n| {{flag|Australia|1901|name=Commonwealth of Australia}}\n| {{flag|New South Wales}}<br />{{flag|Queensland}}<br />{{flagicon image|South Australia Colonial Flag 1876-1904 alternate.svg}} [[South Australia]]<br />{{flag|Tasmania}}<br />{{flag|Victoria}}<br />{{flag|Western Australia|1870}}<br />Also invited:<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Fiji (1883-1908).svg}} [[Colony of Fiji]]<br />{{Flagicon|New Zealand}} [[Colony of New Zealand]]\n| 1901\n| {{yes}}\n| [[Federation of Australia]]\n|-\n|{{flag|South Africa|1910|name=Union of South Africa}}\n|{{flag|Cape Colony|1909}}\n{{flag|South Africa|1875|name=Colony of Natal}}\n\n{{flag|South Africa|1902|name=Orange River Colony}}\n\