idfielder|MF]]\n|'''{{sortname|Anel|Rashkaj}}'''\n|2014\n|2014\u2013\n|3\n|10\n|-\n|rowspan=\"7\"|4\n|[[Defender (association football)|DF]]\n|'''{{sortname|Fidan|Aliti}}'''\n|2020\u2013\n|2017\u2013\n|1\n|21\n|-\n|[[Midfielder|MF]]\n|'''{{sortname|Hekuran|Kryeziu}}'''\n|2019\u2013\n|2015\u2013\n|1\n|19\n|-\n|[[Midfielder|MF]]\n|'''{{sortname|Herolind|Shala}}'''\n|2019\u2013\n|2016\u2013\n|1\n|16\n|-\n|[[Midfielder|MF]]\n|'''{{sortname|Valon|Berisha}}'''\n|2018\u2013\n|2016\u2013\n|1\n|20\n|-\n|[[Midfielder|MF]]\n|{{sortname|Enis|Alushi}}\n|2014\n|2014\u20132017\n|1\n|10\n|-\n|[[Midfielder|MF]]\n|{{sortname|Besnik|Hasi}}\n|2007\n|2007\n|1\n|1\n|-\n|[[Midfielder|MF]]\n|{{sortname|Genc|Hoxha|nolink=1}}\n|1993\n|1993\n|1\n|1\n|}\n\n==Head-to-head records against other countries==\n{{updated|12 January 2019|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://eu-football.info/_matches.php?id=122|title=Kosovo national football team match results|quote=Only matches from 2014 are included|website=eu-football.info}}</ref>}}\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!Opponent\n!{{Abbr|Pld|Played}}\n!{{Abbr|W|Won}}\n!{{Abbr|D|Drawn}}\n!{{Abbr|L|Lost}}\n!{{Abbr|GF|Goals for}}\n!{{Abbr|GA|Goals against}}\n!{{Abbr|GD|Goal difference}}\n!{{Abbr|Win %|Percentage of games won}}\n!Reference\n|-\n!colspan=\"10\"|1942\u201375\n|- bgcolor=\"#BBF3BB\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|Socialist Republic of Bosnia and Herzegovina}} [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n{{WDL|1|1|0|0|for=2|against=1|diff=yes}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"6\"|<ref name=Dizdari/><ref name=Shehu/>\n|- bgcolor=\"#BBF3BB\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|Socialist Republic of Macedonia}} [[North Macedonia national football team|Macedonia]]\n{{WDL|1|1|0|0|for=1|against=0|diff=yes}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#BBF3BB\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|SR Montenegro}} [[Montenegro national football team|Montenegro]]\n{{WDL|1|1|0|0|for=2|agai